    • login

      public boolean login(String username, String password, String phoneNumber, String code)
      Attempts to log in a user using authentication and SMS verification.
      Parameters:
      username - the username to authenticate.
      password - the password associated with the username.
      phoneNumber - the phone number associated with the user.
      code - the verification code to check against the generated code.
      Returns:
      true if the user is successfully authenticated and verified, false otherwise.
